  "body": "I am getting the following error on Teku v23.5.0.\r\n\r\n```shell\r\nUnexpected rejected execution due to full task queue in p2p-async-scheduler-0\r\n``` \r\n\r\nJust before this error I get lots of this warnings\r\n\r\n```shell \r\n WARN  - Discarding gossip message for topic /eth2/824be431/beacon_aggregate_and_proof/ssz_snappy because the signature verification queue is full\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis results in Teku falling out of sync and not attesting anymore. \r\nI am running this setup on Dappnode if it might be of any help.",
