    "body": "Hello @Archethect,\r\nMost probably your node started struggling due to low resources (probably memory) which caused gossip queues to fill up and after a while your node fell out of sync and stopped attesting.\r\n\r\nCan you share how much ram you are giving to teku? (the -Xmx parameter), teku now prints some of these info in the logs at startup.\r\nWhich type of CPU do you have? How many dapps are you running in dappnode?\r\n\r\nLatest 23.6.0 is more resilient when under pressure.",
